  <ab>
    
     <pb n="1r" facs="7"/>
    
    <seg function="title"><milestone unit="left-margin"/>
    <lb n="1"/>tiruvaḷḷuvar kuṟaḷ</seg>

    <seg function="preface"><milestone unit="main-text-area"/><note xml:lang="en">commentary preamble</note>
     <lb n="1"/>Eṇṇiya veṇṇiya veytupa kaṇṇutaṟ
pavaḷa mālvaira payanta
kavaḷa yāṉaiyiṉ kaḻalpaṇi vōrē - 1
Intiraṉ mutaliya viṟaiyavar
      <lb n="2"/>pataṅkaḷu mantami liṉpatu taḻivil vīṭuneṟi yaṟinteytutaṟ kuriya māntāk kuṟitipayappa vuyarntōrā ṉēṭukkappaṭṭa poruṉāṉka
      <lb n="3" break="no"/>vai yaṟamporuḷiṉpavī ṭeṉpaṉavaṟṟuḷ - vīṭepatu cintaiyu moḻiyuñ cellā nilamaittātaliṟṟuṟa vaṟamāki
      <lb n="4" break="no"/>ya kāraṇavakaiyāṟ kūṟappaṭuvatallatilak kaṇvakaiyāṟ kūṟappaṭālaiyi ṉūlkaḷāṟ kūṟappaṭuvaṉa[.] <note xml:lang="en">preface to the commentary ending on <locus facs="9">f2r</locus>, l. 5</note>
      </seg>
    
         <pb n="2v"/><note xml:lang="en">blank</note>

     <pb n="3r" facs="11"/>
    
    <seg function="title"><milestone unit="left-margin"/>
      <lb n="1"/>kuṟaḷ.</seg>
    
    <seg function="incipit"><milestone unit="main-text-area"/>
      <lb n="1"/>
      Akara mutala veḻuttellā māti
pakavaṉ mutaṟṟē yulaku - Etu - 
Akaramākiya mutalaiyuṭaiya veḻuttukkaḷellā matupōlavāti pakavaṉā
      <lb n="2" break="no"/>kiya mutalaiyuṭait tulakameṉṟavāṟu – Itu talaimaipaṟṟivanta veṭuttukkāṭṭuvamai</seg>

<pb n="373r" facs="751"/>
<seg function="explicit"><lb n="4"/>Ūṭutal kāmattiṟ kiṉpa mataṟkiṉpaṅ
kūṭi muyaṅkap peṟiṉ - Etu -
itu kāmanukarccik kiṉpamāvatu ataṉai
    <lb n="5"/>nukartaṟ kuriyārāvā rārāmaipaṟṟit tammuḷūṭutal avvūṭutaṟkiṉpa māvatu ataṉai yaḷavaṟintu nīṅkit tammuṭ kūṭi muyaṅkutal kūṭu
    <lb n="6" break="no"/>māyi ṉammuyakkameṉṟavāṟu – kūṭutalotta vaḷaviḷarātal mutirntu tuṉiyāya vaḻittuṉpam payattalāṉun tāmutirnta pulaviyāya vaḻikkalaviyi
    <lb n="7" break="no"/>ṉpam payamāmaiyāṉu miraṇṭaṟku miṭaiyākiya vaḷavaṟintu nīkkutalāteṉpatu paṟṟik kūṭṭi muyaṅkap peṟiṉeṉṟāṉ avviraṇṭiṉpamum
    
    <pb n="373v" facs="752"/>
    <lb n="1"/>yāṉ peṟṟēṉeṉapatām yīṇṭup piriviṉai vaṭanūṉ matampaṟṟic celavāṟṟāmai vituppup pulaviyeṉa nālvakaiya tākkik kūṟiṉār a
    <lb n="2" break="no"/>ṟṟuṭ celavupirivāṟṟāmai yuḷḷumāṟṟāmai paṭarmelintiraṅkaṉamutaṉiṟai yaḻitalīḷa yavaṟṟuḷḷuvituppuvarvayiṉa vatumpaḷamutaṟ puṇarcci 
    <lb n="3"/>vitumpavīḷu yavaṟṟuḷḷum pulavi neñcoṭu pulattaṉamutalātalu vakaiyīrā yavaṟṟuḷḷuṅ kaṇṭukoḷka - aḵtela vaṭanūlāri
    <lb n="4" break="no"/>vaṟṟuṭaṉē pāvattīṉṉāyaṉīkkattiṉaiyuṅ kūṭṭip piriviṉaiyai vakaitteṉṟārāleṉi ṉaḵtaṟamporuḷiṉpaṅ kiṉeṉum pa
    <lb n="5" break="no"/>yaṉ kaṇāṭuḷāṉṟupaṟṟi yataṉmaiyāṉu muṉivarāṉaiyā ṉorukāl kutōr kuṟṟattuḷatāvatalla tulakiyal pāyvārāmaiyā
    <lb n="6" break="no"/>ṉu mīṇṭoḻikkappaṭṭateṉka - <g ref="#pattu"/> -</seg> <seg function="total-stanzas">Āka - <g ref="#āyiram"/>3<g ref="#nūru"/>3<g ref="#pattu"/> -</seg> <seg function="completion-statement">kāmattuppāl muṭintatu -</seg> <seg function="total-stanzas">Āka muppālukkum atikāram - <g ref="#nūṟu"/>3<g ref="#pattu"/>3 <g ref="#pcs"/> </seg> <seg function="completion-statement">muṟṟum <g ref="#pcl"/></seg>
    </ab>
